    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ 425\u00b0F/ Gas 6</p> <p>Peel and cut the <strong>sweet potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into chips</p> <p>Add the\u00a0<strong>sweet potato chips</strong>\u00a0to a baking tray with a drizzle of\u00a0<strong>vegetable oil\u00a0</strong>and a generous pinch of\u00a0<strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p> <p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp \u00a0</p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p> <p>Slice 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> discs from the\u00a0<strong>cucumber </strong>(these will go in your sandwich later!)</p> <p>Slice the <strong>remaining cucumber</strong>\u00a0in half lengthways, then slice the halves into wedges</p> <p>Chop the <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped dill</strong>, <strong>black</strong>\u00a0<strong>mustard seeds</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, a splash of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl and stir until dissolved</p> <p>Add <strong>all</strong> of the\u00a0<strong>sliced\u00a0cucumber</strong> to the vinegar, give everything a good mix up and set aside \u2013 this is your <strong>pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice the\u00a0<strong>cheddar cheese</strong>\u00a0in quarters lengthways</p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong>\u00a0ciabatta rolls\u00a0</strong>in half</p> <p>Spread\u00a0the <strong>ciabatta base</strong> with the\u00a0<strong>mustard ketchup</strong></p> <p>Add the <strong>shredded</strong>\u00a0<strong>ham hock</strong>\u00a0to the\u00a0<strong>ciabatta base</strong>,\u00a0and top\u00a0with the\u00a0<strong>cheddar cheese\u00a0</strong>and add to a baking tray with the <strong>ciabatta lids</strong> (cut side up)</p> <p>Put the tray in the oven for 3-4 mins or until the cheese has melted</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the cheese has melted, remove the tray from the oven and spread<strong>\u00a0mayonnaise</strong> over the <strong>ciabatta lids</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Layer the\u00a0<strong>pickled cucumber discs</strong>\u00a0on top of the <strong>melted cheese</strong> and top with the <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>\u2013 this is your<strong>\u00a0New York melt</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/new-york-style-ham-and-cheese-melt/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>New York melt</strong>\u00a0with the <strong>sweet potato chips</strong>\u00a0and remaining\u00a0<strong>pickled cucumber</strong>\u00a0<strong>wedges</strong> to the side</p> <p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
